{"tid":1400814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[法律JJ非三毛] 火攻 成本高效用低 唔好送頭呀","createTime":"2019-08-03T13:49:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T15:02:35.000Z","uid":58721,"like":139,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"891ae0e81175191f8cdf78ff3bb3e00713de6222","tid":1400814,"uid":58721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:49:52.000Z","msg":"附上學生證 證明唔係三毛非分化<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iLF39Zq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiLF39Zq.jpg&h=2db420f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 縱火係法律上 係同謀殺強姦一樣咁大罪</span></strong><br />\n最高可以判終身<br />\n縱火好難打甩<br />\n只要證明到係有心放火就得<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">第200章《刑事罪行條例》 第60條摧毀或損壞財產<br />\n(2)任何人無合法辯解而摧毀或損壞任何財產(不論是屬於其本人或他人的) &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(b)意圖藉摧毀或損壞財產以危害他人生命或罔顧他人生命是否會因而受到危害，<br />\n即屬犯罪。<br />\n(3)用火摧毀或損壞財產而犯本條所訂罪行者，須被控以縱火。<br />\n<br />\n63.罪行的懲處<br />\n(1)任何人犯第60條所訂的縱火的罪行或第60(2)條所訂的罪行(不論是否屬縱火)，一經循公訴程序定罪，可處終身監禁。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 縱火喱條罪性質上同非法集結同暴動唔同</span></strong><br />\n當我地爭取到5大訴求唔告義士<br />\n縱火極有可能會照告<br />\n我地唔係講好要齊上齊落嫁咩<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>3. 消防效率咁高 放幾分鐘火就救熄啦</strong></span><br />\n為幾分鐘火 俾人判終身 值咩?<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">4. 如果太大火 好易傷及無辜市民 同我地成日屌警察係民居放催淚彈有咩分別</span></strong><br />\n天琦封信提我地: 我們必須警惕每一言一行，到底會更接近目標，還是距離更遠呢？<br />\n我相信 如果大家放火而有任何死傷 一定會令我地距離目標更遠<br />\n<br />\n各位義士唔好送頭呀"},{"pid":"5dd7e00902098c14016777e569e4fdbcc35e7c3c","tid":1400814,"uid":58721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:50:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"db884feed92764a6b754d7c0530d6aa42c1ab331","tid":1400814,"uid":26813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:51:48.000Z","msg":"sorry借位宣傳<br />\n推俾前線手足睇！<br />\n<br />\n［前線路障快閃團］簡易快速拆鐵欄攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400592</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c681f3430f0bb7cfc682cb8a65e37e342cbced62","tid":1400814,"uid":138409,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:52:03.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n你話出水炮車 就話用雞尾酒姐<br />\n依家似乎未到時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa15e95e9d4a4c21f1aa8e5ff9db5acbc9964ee","tid":1400814,"uid":263186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:54:38.000Z","msg":"尖沙咀快走，又爆動罪 唔值"},{"pid":"db31e8b93bd895bcc60bcdb9bd0ef27cd91e7ec3","tid":1400814,"uid":268537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:55:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6b42a94d577a3c7b4acc82bb385e14a9c2cc19bf","tid":1400814,"uid":37504,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:55:31.000Z","msg":"而家告暴動都莫須有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲講法律"},{"pid":"8457358d3fa248cd3e393df9261c6e18e1197461","tid":1400814,"uid":278391,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:56:03.000Z","msg":"火有時唔係你控制到的<br />\n<br />\n仲有過埋85先啦"},{"pid":"af455bd5fcd6c5edb6338e721a1d5387501e6969","tid":1400814,"uid":58721,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"6b42a94d577a3c7b4acc82bb385e14a9c2cc19bf","tid":1400814,"uid":37504,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:55:31.000Z","msg":"而家告暴動都莫須有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲講法律"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:01:36.000Z","msg":"但縱火唔係莫須有<br />\n有放就會入罪<br />\n甚至放個幾分鐘就俾人救熄嘅火都係縱火<br />\n仲要坐終身呀<br />\n<br />\n你仲鼓勵義士放火<br />\n係咪佢地放完 你代佢地坐終身呀"},{"pid":"0cdec345bd542e7d44d15ed02041f0f7f2263de9","tid":1400814,"uid":58721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:12:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a043ce1639741961bd5e93c40304850091997662","tid":1400814,"uid":58721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:12:54.00